<D>__{i have written to edward, miss dashwood, and yet i do not know how much i may see of him. secrecy is vital he will never be able to call.}
<C>__{elinor}
<D>__{i should imagine not.}
<C>__{lucy}
<D>__{it is so hard. i believe my only comfort has been the constancy of his affection.}
<C>__{elinor}
<D>__{you are fortunate, over such a lengthy engagement, never to have had any doubts on that score.}
